Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:30.32,alternazev_ep,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,348)}Hokuto {\alpha&HFF&}Juu{\alpha&HFF&}ha {\alpha&HFF&}Zan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:30.44,alternazev_ep,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,348)}Hokuto Juu{\alpha&HFF&}ha {\alpha&HFF&}Zan
